lines.text: Eh mere diley nadan, tu gum se na gabrana, ik din to samaj lenghi duniya tera apsana... O my dear heart, do not be afraid of sorrow for one day this world will understand your plight...
Main khush naseeb mujko kisika pyar mila, bada haseen mere dil ka razdar mila... I am fortunate that I have receive someone's love, someone beautiful is my soulmate...
